# S03-T10: Fullscreen Tactical Mode

## Objective
Provide a one-touch fullscreen mode that hides browser chrome and maximizes video real estate.

## Acceptance Criteria
- `useFullscreen()` hook wrapping `requestFullscreen` / Tauri window API.
- Top-bar fullscreen toggle (icon button, min 48×48px).
- Auto-hide non-critical HUD slots after 5s idle (mouse/touch).
- ESC exits fullscreen; gesture (S05-T04 swipe-down) also exits.

## Steps
1. Implement `useFullscreen()` with browser + Tauri branches via `bridge.ts`.
2. Add `IdleTimer` utility (resets on pointer/touch).
3. Wire to slot visibility map (HUD preset overlay).
4. Add CSS class `.fullscreen-mode` to AppShell.

## Invariants
- Critical alerts (pink) NEVER auto-hide.
- Crosshair and target overlay remain visible in all states.
- Exit gesture fires within 200ms of input.
